{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"30f0a258aa","title":"李先念在北京对外贸易学院的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"db6ee11b1a","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":17,"articleId":"30f0a258aa","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"李先念","id":"33f01f9c5a","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"637e61c517","name":"李先念"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"88839f874f","type":"title","text":"李先念在北京对外贸易学院的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f133ce9976","type":"paragraph","text":"1、打破一切旧框框，集中力量炮打司令部。所谓的炮打司令部，就是党组、公司经理、司长、局长、特别是党组。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f0b09197c","type":"paragraph","text":"2、只许炮打司令部，不许炮打群众。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"009bfc4037","type":"paragraph","text":"3、学习十六条，运用十六条，在运动中学，在炮打司令部中学。活学活用，也只有这样，才能形成左派队伍，要引导群众去学习。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e52195c30d","type":"paragraph","text":"4、立即检查有没有打击左派群众，斗争群众的现象，各部门不要漫不经心。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c0cce389ce","type":"paragraph","text":"5、文化革命与日常工作关系。必须高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗，以阶级斗争为纲，不要采取折衷主义的态度，要争取双丰收。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed39b5a752","type":"paragraph","text":"6、文革筹委会立即成立起来。成立以后，可以今天成立明天推翻，现在好多筹委会被推翻了。因为群众就是不拥护嘛。可以全部推翻，也可以推翻一个，补选一个，要充分发挥民主。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0f52bb6047","type":"paragraph","text":"3、学习十六条，运用十六条，在运动中学，在炮打司令部中学。活学活用，也只有这样，才能形成左派队伍，要引导群众去学习。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"292020ca80","type":"paragraph","text":"5、文化革命与日常工作关系。必须高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗，以阶级斗争为纲，不要采取折衷主义的态度，要争取双丰收。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c8aea9173","type":"paragraph","text":"1、打破一切旧框框，集中力量炮打司令部。所谓的炮打司令部，就是党组、公司经理、司长、局长、特别是党组。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b83cb35c95","type":"paragraph","text":"4、立即检查有没有打击左派群众，斗争群众的现象，各部门不要漫不经心。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bccb0756d8","type":"paragraph","text":"2、只许炮打司令部，不许炮打群众。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2700ec8ab","type":"title","text":"李先念在北京对外贸易学院的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7012f5b0c","type":"paragraph","text":"6、文革筹委会立即成立起来。成立以后，可以今天成立明天推翻，现在好多筹委会被推翻了。因为群众就是不拥护嘛。可以全部推翻，也可以推翻一个，补选一个，要充分发挥民主。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"30f0a258aa","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}